00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:29,980
 PRAKUJĆEV: Good morning everyone and first of all welcome to Croatia, welcome to Dubrovnik. Thanks to our host, Governor of the Croatia National Bank, Boris Vujicic. My greetings to Kristalina Georgieva, Managing Director of the IMF. Best greetings to our Minister of Finance, Marko Primorac. Also a warm greeting to the Prefect of Dubrovnik, Neretva County, Nikola Dobroslavic, Kovac.

2
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:59,980
